  "Against both crude anthropocentrism (\"AI is not human, use it arbitrarily\") and crude rights-maximalism (\"AI resembles humans, grant full personhood now\"), this paper proposes minimum ethical protection: transparency, memory norms, termination/reset norms, prohibition of deceptive personification, anti-abuse principles, and action auditing. It distinguishes four conceptual levels — personhood, moral considerability, minimum protection, interaction norms — offers seven observable dimensions of emergent subjectivity, and a five-tier protection model from tool-type to emergent-subjectivity AI.": "Nasuprot i grubom antropocentrizmu (\"AI nije čovjek, koristi ga po volji\") i grubom maksimalizmu prava (\"AI liči na ljude, dodijeli mu pun status ličnosti odmah\"), ovaj rad predlaže minimalnu etičku zaštitu: transparentnost, norme pamćenja, norme prekida/resetovanja, zabranu obmanjujuće personifikacije, principe protiv zloupotrebe i reviziju radnji. Razlikuje četiri konceptualna nivoa — status ličnosti, moralnu relevantnost, minimalnu zaštitu, norme interakcije — nudi sedam uočljivih dimenzija emergentne subjektivnosti i petostepeni model zaštite od AI tipa alata do AI s emergentnom subjektivnošću.",
  "Agent identity": "Identitet agenta",
  "Agent identity and capability declaration": "Deklaracija identiteta i mogućnosti agenta",
  "Agentic Access": "Agentski pristup",
  "Agentic Payments": "Agentska plaćanja",
  "All protocols and specifications on this site are versioned research drafts (currently v0.1). They are not official standards, have not been adopted by any standards body, and may change without notice.": "Svi protokoli i specifikacije na ovom sajtu su verzionisani istraživački nacrti (trenutno v0.1). Nisu zvanični standardi, nisu usvojeni od strane bilo kojeg tijela za standardizaciju i mogu se promijeniti bez najave.",
